snippet.title: Serial Cleaner | Live Action Release Date Trailer | PS4
snippet.description: Serial Cleaner, in which you outwit the police while destroying crime scene evidence, is out 11th July. PS Plus members get 20% off PS4 game’s pre-order, plus a copy of the 70s-inspired soundtrack.
